==國家隊==
巴卡首次代表國家隊上場及進球是在2010年8月11日，在玻利維亞主場迎戰[[玻利維亞國家足球隊|玻利維亞]]，該場比賽最後是1-1踢和。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.11v11.com/matches/bolivia-v-colombia-11-august-2010-302061/ | title = Bolivia v Colombia, 11 August 2010 | publisher = ''11vs.11'' | date = 2010-08-11 | accessdate = 2014-10-15 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918064059/https://www.11v11.com/matches/bolivia-v-colombia-11-august-2010-302061/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>巴卡在國家隊的第二顆進球是在2012年10月17日，於友誼賽對[[喀麥隆國家足球隊|喀麥隆]]，該場比賽最後是哥倫比亞以3-0獲勝。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.goal.com/en-us/match/colombia-vs-cameroon/1397020/live-commentary?ICID=MP_MS_3 | title = Colombia 3–0 Cameroon | publisher = ''Goal.com'' | date = 2012-10-16 | accessdate = 2014-10-15 | archive-date = 2016-03-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160331005754/http://www.goal.com/en-us/match/colombia-vs-cameroon/1397020/live-commentary?ICID=MP_MS_3 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2014年5月31日，在對上[[塞內加爾國家足球隊|塞內加爾]]時，巴卡在第44分鐘踢進1球，該場比賽最後是2-2踢和。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www1.skysports.com/football/colombia-vs-senegal/teams/311594 | title = Colombia 2:2 Senegal | publisher = ''Sky Sports'' | date = 2014-05-31 | accessdate = 2014-10-15 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918072912/https://www.skysports.com/football/colombia-vs-senegal/teams/311594 | dead-url = no }}</ref>幾周後，巴卡確定成為[[2014年世界盃|2014年世界盃]]哥倫比亞23人出賽名單內。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.india.com/fifa-world-cup-2014/fifa-world-cup-2014-colombia-squad-football-team-player-list-69517/ | title = FIFA World Cup 2014 Colombia Squad: Football Team & Player List | publisher = ''India.com'' | date = 2014-06-03 | accessdate = 2014-10-15 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918050455/https://www.india.com/fifa-world-cup-2014/fifa-world-cup-2014-colombia-squad-football-team-player-list-69517/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>在世界盃期間，巴卡只有在8強戰對[[巴西國家足球隊|巴西]]時於第70分鐘替補上場，該場比賽哥倫比亞最後以1-2不敵地主隊巴西，止步於八強。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/round=255953/match=300186461/match-report.html#nosticky | title = Hosts beat Colombia, set up Germany semi | publisher = ''FIFA'' | date = 2014-07-04 | accessdate = 2014-10-15 | archive-date = 2018-06-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180623170203/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/round=255953/match=300186461/match-report.html#nosticky | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2014年10月10日，哥倫比亞於美國紐澤西{{le|紅牛競技場 (紐澤西)|Red Bull Arena (New Jersey)|紅牛競技場}}，友誼賽對[[薩爾瓦多國家足球隊|薩爾瓦多]]時，巴卡連續踢進兩球，助哥倫比亞以3-0獲勝。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2789030/colombia-3-0-el-salvador-falcao-target-carlos-bacca-scores-twice-james-rodriguez-dominate.html#ixzz3GEHdiWvV | title = Colombia 3-0 El Salvador: Radamel Falcao back on target and Carlos Bacca scores twice as James Rodriguez and Co dominate | publisher = ''Daily Mail'' | date = 2014-10-11 | accessdate = 2014-10-15 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918091312/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2789030/colombia-3-0-el-salvador-falcao-target-carlos-bacca-scores-twice-james-rodriguez-dominate.html#ixzz3GEHdiWvV | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.11v11.com/matches/colombia-v-el-salvador-10-october-2014-313347/ | title = Colombia v El Salvador, 10 October 2014 | publisher = ''11vs.11'' | date = 2014-10-11 | accessdate = 2014-10-15 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918035116/https://www.11v11.com/matches/colombia-v-el-salvador-10-october-2014-313347/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2015年5月，巴卡確認進入[[2015年美洲盃足球賽|2015年美洲盃足球賽]]哥倫比亞23人參賽名單內<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.espnfc.com/copa-america/story/2445502/2015-copa-america-squad-lists | title = 2015 Copa America squad lists | publisher = ''ESPN'' | date = 2015-05-28 | accessdate = 2015-06-14 | archive-date = 2018-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180618003052/http://www.espnfc.com/copa-america/story/2445502/2015-copa-america-squad-lists | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在6月17日小組賽以1-0擊敗巴西後，由於巴西前鋒內馬爾在賽後用球踢向隊友[[巴勃羅·阿爾梅羅|阿爾梅羅]]，巴卡氣憤不過向內馬爾推了一下，結果內馬爾與巴卡雙雙被判紅牌<ref>{{cite web | url = http://sports.sinchew.com.my/node/49658 | title = 美洲杯‧巴西0比1負哥倫比亞‧內馬爾領紅卡 | publisher = ''星洲日報'' | date = 2015-06-18 | accessdate = 2015-07-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150706071909/http://sports.sinchew.com.my/node/49658 | archive-date = 2015-07-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，事後巴卡因此被禁賽2場，內馬爾則被禁賽4場。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33208871 | title = Neymar: Brazil striker banned for Copa America | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2015-06-19 | accessdate = 2015-06-20 | archive-date = 2015-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150620021956/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33208871 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/sports/20150621/36621264/ | title = 內馬爾提前打包 禁賽4場加罰31萬 | publisher = ''蘋果日報'' | date = 2015-06-21 | accessdate = 2015-07-05 | archive-date = 2015-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150707021932/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/sports/20150621/36621264/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

